com.mobius.vdrapi.callbacks
Interface INeedFullLoginCredentials

All Known Implementing Classes:
CreatePageGroupCommand, FindCommand, GotoCommand, LocateNodeCommand
public interface INeedFullLoginCredentials

A class implements INeedFullLoginCredentials to indicate that it may need to acquire login credentials, security, and ticket information for a particular document server.

Note: Classes that do not require security or ticket information should implement INeedLoginCredentials instead. If both interfaces are implemented, a MultipleCallbacksSetException is thrown.
